=== Assessment Schedule

    - *Baseline*: TSPO-PET imaging, detailed clinical assessment, 6-month pre-baseline PEM diary retrospective review
    - *6 months*: TSPO-PET imaging, PEM diary review, functional assessment
    - *12 months*: TSPO-PET imaging, comprehensive clinical and biomarker assessment
    - *Continuous*: Electronic PEM crash diary with severity ratings (1–10 scale), recovery duration documentation


